\f2\'b7\tab\f1 one or two \b Recommended Statistics\b0  that should ideally be higher than average for characters of that Archetype;\par
\f2\'b7\tab\f1 a starting \b Number of Bonds\b0  (usually between 2 and 5);\par
\f2\'b7\tab\f1 a \b Starting Resources\b0  rating (usually between 2 and 5);\par
